IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Host imap.mailbox.org
UserCmd "cat $HOME/.password-store/.defaults/username"
PassCmd "pass show www/mail/mailbox.org/password"
TLSType IMAPS

MaildirStore mailbox-local
Path  ~/.mail/mailbox/
Inbox ~/.mail/mailbox/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel mailbox
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All

IMAPStore proton-remote
Host localhost
Port 1143
UserCmd "pass show www/mail/proton.me/username"
PassCmd "pass show www/mail/proton.me/bridge"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType None

MaildirStore proton-local
Path  ~/.mail/proton/
Inbox ~/.mail/proton/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel proton
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All
